name: Less interrupting
description:
That night when i'm looking at one of my friend listening for around 30 minutes non-stop without interrupting, I immediately pulled out my camera and took a pic. Then i realized the hardest thing is learning to shut our mouth and open our ears!
Too often humans stumble around trying to pursue their own agendas and do not take the time to absorb and understand.
Humans may think they are communicating at a higher level thanks to all the wonders of the world. Yet, so few of them connect in a meaningful way. It is sad because it is so empty of real emotion.
True listening enhance our relationships, and they attract people.
